public abstract class CommunityProfileOMASAPIResponse extends FFDCResponseBase
CommunityProfileOMASAPIResponse provides a common header for Community Profile OMAS managed rest to its REST API. It manages information about exceptions. If no exception has been raised exceptionClassName is null.
